					<div class="post-info">
						<p>
							<span class="time">July 7, 2012</span>
															<span class="author">by <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/author/mktgeistmike/" title="Posts by mktgeistmike" rel="author">mktgeistmike</a></span>
																						<span class="post-comments"><a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/2012/07/07/keiser-report-e309-jp-morgans-9-billion-problem/#respond" title="Comment on Keiser Report [E309] &#8211; JP Morgan&#8217;s $9 Billion&nbsp;Problem">Leave a comment</a></span>
