					<h2><a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/2012/07/04/jim-rogers-war-and-the-financial-mafia-libor-centrals-banks-and-jp-morgan/">Jim Rogers, War and the Financial Mafia &#8211; LIBOR, Centrals Banks and JP&nbsp;Morgan</a></h2>

					<div class="post-info">
						<p>
							<span class="time">July 4, 2012</span>
															<span class="author">by <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/author/mktgeistmike/" title="Posts by mktgeistmike" rel="author">mktgeistmike</a></span>
																						<span class="post-comments"><a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/2012/07/04/jim-rogers-war-and-the-financial-mafia-libor-centrals-banks-and-jp-morgan/#respond" title="Comment on Jim Rogers, War and the Financial Mafia &#8211; LIBOR, Centrals Banks and JP&nbsp;Morgan">Leave a comment</a></span>
