					<div class="post-info">
						<p>
							<span class="time">June 27, 2012</span>
															<span class="author">by <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/author/mktgeistmike/" title="Posts by mktgeistmike" rel="author">mktgeistmike</a></span>
																						<span class="post-comments"><a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/2012/06/27/jp-morgan-managers-being-told-trade-loss-is-9-billion-teri-buhl/#respond" title="Comment on JP Morgan Managers Being Told Trade Loss is $9 Billion [Teri&nbsp;Buhl]">Leave a comment</a></span>
